sources.title: Lady Frankenstein (1971 Horror) Only The Monster She Created Could Fulfill Her Ambition! 4K
sources.description:
After Baron Frankenstein's tragic death, his daughter Tania and assistant Dr. Marshall continue his groundbreaking experiments. As their creation unleashes chaos, Tania devises a plan to save their work.

Original title: La Figlia di Frankenstein (1971)
Alternative title: Lady Frankenstein

Directors: Mel Welles, Aureliano Luppi
Writers: Umberto Borsato, Egidio Gelso, Aureliano Luppi

Main cast:
Joseph Cotten – Baron Frankenstein
Rosalba Neri – Dr. Tania Frankenstein
Paul Muller – Dr. Charles Marshall
Herbert Fux – Tom Lynch, the graverobber
Marino Masé – Thomas Stack
Mickey Hargitay – Captain Harris

Genres: Horror, Science Fiction, Monster movie
Release date: October 22, 1971 (Italy)
Filming location: Rome, Italy

Uncensored version: https://youtu.be/EGN9xHsVO9w
